Containeruniface_104nix1719658677845.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nix1719658677845.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nix1719658677845.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rcp1665703009083\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $paintedocc\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rcp1665703009083___paintedocc_280108\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the number of occurrences the specified entity drawn (painted) on the foForm or Report.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__topic_d87539e1_d87540e1_d87541e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__p_d87542e1_d87543e1_d87544e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$paintedocc</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__section_w1071ab1b7b5_w1072ab1b7_w1073ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__p_d87545e1_d87546e1_d87547e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$paintedocc (CUSTOMER)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__topic_d58287e1_d58288e1_d58289e1_d58290e1_d58291e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d222519e84\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__topic_d58292e1_d58293e1_d58294e1_d58295e1_d58296e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d222519e138\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$paintedocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1__entry__1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist or is not painted on the component\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rcp1665703009083__table_d9356e1_d9357e1_d9358e1__entry__2\">\n Number of occurrences painted for the specified entity.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__topic_d58297e1_d58298e1_d58299e1_d58300e1_d58301e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d222519e197\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__p_d87557e1_d87558e1_d87559e1\">Use in Form and Report components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__section_mcp_c1y_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d222519e206\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$paintedocc</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">This example shows a form on which occurrences of entity CUSTOMER have\n               been drawn in three rows and two columns. In this case,\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">$paintedocc(CUSTOMER)</code> returns 6, the total number of\n               occurrences.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__fig_mzh_d1y_wbc\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Multiple Occurrences Painted on a Form</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Multiple occurrences painted on a form\" class=\"image\" id=\"rcp1665703009083__image_nzh_d1y_wbc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/fig14_2.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hbo1720163290270.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>print</a><p>Activate printing.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rch1665702606837.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Printing Character Sets</a><p>To print, choose the device translation table that is specific for the character set.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mfh1719680957014.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$printing</a><p>Return a status indicating whether the current component is printing.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422472\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422472\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$paintedocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $paintedocc Return the number of occurrences the specified entity drawn (painted) on the foForm or Report. $paintedocc { ( Entity ) } Example: $paintedocc (CUSTOMER) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $paintedocc Value Meaning \"\" Entity does not exist or is not painted on the component >0 Number of occurrences painted for the specified entity. Use Use in Form and Report components. Example: Using $paintedocc This example shows a form on which occurrences of entity CUSTOMER have been drawn in three rows and two columns. In this case, $paintedocc(CUSTOMER) returns 6, the total number of occurrences. Figure 1. Multiple Occurrences Painted on a Form Related Links print Activate printing. Printing Character Sets To print, choose the device translation table that is specific for the character set. $printing Return a status indicating whether the current component is printing. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}